  "response": "To determine how much money you owe your housemate, you'll need to consider a few factors, such as:\n\n1. Rent Contribution: How much rent you agreed to share.\n2. Utility Bills: Any shared expenses for electricity, gas, water, internet, etc.\n3. Shared Groceries or Supplies: If you split the cost of food or household items.\n4. Previous Payments: Any payments you've already made or reimbursements owed.\n\nIf you provide some details about these factors, I can help you calculate how much you owe your housemate.",
